<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-29-0647 </DOCNO><TEXT>In an annual survey of Manitoba's petroleum industry, data are presentedon oil lease and reservation sales, geophysical activity, explorationand drilling activity, production, exports to other provinces and USA,oil prices and sales value, royalties and taxes, direct revenues fromoil explorationa nd development, reserves, industry expenditures, andoil fields. Throughout the report, explanations are given of the itemscovered. Descriptions are made of new developments, the oil market, oilpolicies, incentive programs, and industrial activities. A forecast forthe following year is outlined. 18 figs., 19 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>